title: 334: Michelle’s Bachelorette Recap: FANTASY SUITES (Producers are PANICKING!)
itunes:title: 334: Michelle’s Bachelorette Recap: FANTASY SUITES (Producers are PANICKING!)
description:
Bekah and Jess are here to recap Michelle’s “Fantasy Suites” episode (aka Overnights) - and WOW were they thrown for a loop! They chat all about Brandon, Joe, and Nayte’s overnight dates - who they thought would go home, who they think will leave with Michelle, massive questions they have about unseen moments, concerns they have, who is ready for marriage, producers panicking, big shocks, and much more!
